OL,3,C#154 million to be invested in
OL,4,Cplutonium disposal in Cumbria
OL,6,FThe government is planning to invest
OL,7,F#154 million into plutonium disposal
OL,8,Fin Cumbria, which could support around
OL,9,F100 jobs.
OL,11,FThe money will be used by the Nuclear
OL,12,FDecommissioning Authority (NDA) to
OL,13,Fallow them to dispose of tonnes of
OL,14,Fradioactive plutonium.
OL,16,FCurrently, plutonium produced in
OL,17,Fcivilian nuclear power reactors in the
OL,18,FUK is stored at Sellafield in West
OL,19,FCumbria.
