OL,3,C#154 million to be invested in
OL,4,Cplutonium disposal in Cumbria
OL,6,FThe government decided to immobilise
OL,7,Fthe material earlier this year, which
OL,8,Fwill put the material beyond reach and
OL,9,Fmitigates some of the long term risks.
OL,11,FThis majority of the 100 jobs are
OL,12,Fbased in Cumbria and two new state-of-
OL,13,Fthe-art laboratories are being
OL,14,Finstalled at Sellafield to develop
OL,15,Ftechnology to assist with the
OL,16,Fimmobilisation process.
