OL,3,C#154 million to be invested in
OL,4,Cplutonium disposal in Cumbria
OL,6,FNDA Group CEO, David Peattie, said:
OL,7,F"The NDA group is already leading the
OL,8,Fway in nuclear decommissioning and
OL,9,Fsafely managing the UK's most
OL,10,Fhazardous radioactive materials.
OL,12,F"This government investment will allow
OL,13,Fus to drive forward this important
OL,14,Fnational policy, building cutting edge
OL,15,Ffacilities and growing world-leading
OL,16,Fexpertise and capability in plutonium
OL,17,Fimmobilisation, providing a safe,
OL,18,Fsecure and permanent solution.
