OL,3,C#154 million to be invested in
OL,4,Cplutonium disposal in Cumbria
OL,6,F"It's a strong vote of confidence in
OL,7,Four ability to safely, securely, and
OL,8,Fsustainably deal with the UK's civil
OL,9,Fnuclear legacy to benefit future
OL,10,Fgenerations."
OL,12,FWork will take place over the next
OL,13,Ffive years.
OL,15,FMinister for Energy Michael Shanks
OL,16,Fsaid: "Cumbria has a proud nuclear
OL,17,Fhistory, and this new investment will
OL,18,Funlock pioneering technology to manage
OL,19,Four nuclear waste.
